{"type": "article", "id": 3285, "title": "水井玻璃灯具", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-05T08:33:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232950svwCWGTOufMRA16e.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自斯洛伐克的设计师 Štefan Nosko 与 Katarina Beliekova 最近设计出了一款名为 Well 的玻璃灯具，灵感源于传统的水井，灯绳相当于原先井绳的功能，以此来用手动的方式改变灯泡在玻璃容器中的位置。玻璃容器外部用渐变的蓝色或磨砂来装饰，<span>呈现出灯泡落入水中一般的效果</span>。手柄部分由枫木与铜结合制成，灯泡插座则选用了黄铜材质，使得底座更加稳固，更方便灯绳做上下直线运动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232948c3EFzosT79w6Dly5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232948TkJi81ebnfUcVOLz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232948YrsoeDxzMw8JqtvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232949GfuTUNgWthVIQb2Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052329499N31WZ6Lb5jeFwGU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}